    <item>
      <title>股价暴跌，遥远的 Capri 突然上市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/far-off-capri-put-options-suddenly-in-play-as-shares-plunge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在法官阻止了这家包袋制造商与 Tapestry Inc. 的合并提议后，Capri Holdings Ltd. 的股价在售后交易中暴跌逾 50%，其远低于市场的看跌期权从几乎一文不值变成了潜在价值超过 200 万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/far-off-capri-put-options-suddenly-in-play-as-shares-plunge</guid>
